name: Spacer-Ranger-The Destination
description:
SPACE RANGER-THE DESTINATION

Welcome to Spacer Ranger the game have new awesome gameplay of the destination of player spacer craft .The game contains different types of level with and number of enemy and obstacles.

                                                                                 STORY

Spacer Ranger has lost her space town while during the mission due to lost signal to the town and he can not find the destiny of the path and now your mission is to complete all the level for the space ranger to  reach ranger the ranger destination.

                                                                      Game Key Function

1. Spacebar - to push the space craft and activate engine.

2. A - To move left side.

3. D -  To move Right Side.

4. W -Fire the Laser on the Enemy while the laser status active.

5. Don not close system while in the Play Mode.
